snippet.title: JUICE - Colorfiction - Demo out Now!
snippet.description:
WISHLIST ON STEAM! play the demo: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2844430/Juice
Get ready for the Apocalypse in this action-packed dual narrative! Witness the crimson rampage of a vicious Monster versus the valiant last stand of a lone Survivor. Who will emerge Victorious?
